$mod+g                focus FIREFOX
$mod+p                RESIZE  MODE
$mod+y                SYSTEM  MODE
$mod+z                DISPLAY MODE
$mod+apostrophe       split horizontal and execute terminal
$mod+slash            split vertical and execute terminal
